pageContext.claim: “In the United States, these deals [with Japan] are a game changer for our farmers and our ranchers -- we love our farmers and we love our ranchers; we've been working very hard on this -- providing them with significantly enhanced access to a critical foreign market.”
pageContext.analysis: Trump struck a limited trade agreement with Japan that many experts said will not help farmers make up for their substantial losses from Trump's trade war with China.
